# Development experience — dev seed data

[`src/main/resources/dev-import.sql`](../../src/main/resources/dev-import.sql) runs on every `%dev` startup via [`DatabaseDevSetup`](../../src/main/java/dev/vepo/passport/shared/infra/DatabaseDevSetup.java).

## Run

```bash
./mvnw quarkus:dev
```

Backoffice: `ng serve --proxy-config src/proxy.conf.json` → login `cto-boss` / `qwas1234`.

## When adding features

Extend dev-import with profiles, roles, or users that exercise the feature. Stable usernames: `cto-boss`, `junior`, `guest-user`.

## Never

- Ship admin features with no dev persona to test them.
- Put production credentials in dev-import.

See [dev-import-sql-safety.mdc](dev-import-sql-safety.mdc).
